strings:
<voice_0x01001CB7><se_high>Princess Medea: Is the world coming to an end!?
What are we going to do!?
What are we going to do!?

<voice_0x01001CB8><se_high>Princess Medea: I...I'm so sorry.
I lost control for a moment.

<voice_0x01001CB9><se_high>Princess Medea: No matter how frightened I am, I want you
to know that I'll follow you to the ends of
the earth.
<voice_0x01001CBA><se_high>Princess Medea: I'll do whatever it takes to defeat Rhapthorne!

<voice_0x01001CBB><se_high>Princess Medea: As far as I'm concerned, our battle against
Rhapthorne began the day Dhoulmagus took
the sceptre.

<voice_0x01001CBC><se_high>Princess Medea: Now the sky is the colour of fire,
and the entire world is living in fear...

<voice_0x01001CBD><se_high>Princess Medea: This isn't just about Trodain any more.
Everyone's fate is in your hands, <hero>.
<voice_0x01001CBE><se_high>Princess Medea: And whatever happens, I'll stay by your side <hero>, always!
